# 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\
\
## Problem Statement\
The book generation system produces architecturally correct but repetitive content. The repetition is not a "writing quality" issue \'97 it's a **governance gap**. The system allows unlimited re-explanation and demonstration of insights within chapters.\
\
## Root Cause\
Governors are defined but **not enforced at runtime**. The template contains the repetition; manual editing cannot fix this sustainably.\
\
## Solution\
Enable governor enforcement, run validators, delete flagged beats from template, regenerate. No manual prose edits.\
\
## Definition of Done\
> Regenerated book has 0 duplicate blocks, demo count within cap, explain count within cap, and no truncation artifacts \'97 with no manual edits.\
\
---\
\
# 2. GOVERNOR DEFINITIONS\
\
## 2.1 Governor A: Explain Cap (Anti-Chant / Anti-Reteach)\
\
### Purpose\
Prevents the same insight from being conceptually taught multiple times within a chapter.\
\
### Rule\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f11 \cf0 Per insight, per chapter:\
  EXPLAIN beats allowed: 1\
  Violation: FAIL (hard block)
\f0 \
\
### What It Fixes\
| Chapter | Problem | Beat IDs to Flag |\
|---------|---------|------------------|\
| 4 | "Same feeling. Different relationship." repeated 4x | beat_05, beat_06, beat_07 |\
| 6 | Opening "You've been fighting a war" repeated twice | beat_01 (duplicate) |\
| 9
\f7 \uc0\u8594 
\f0 10 | Slip content re-explained in Ch10 | ch10_beat_00, ch10_beat_01, ch10_beat_02, ch10_beat_03 |\
| 11 | Identity statements pile up (11 total) | beat_02 excess items |\
\
### Config\

\f11 yaml\
governors:\
  explain_cap:\
    enabled: true\
    max_per_insight_per_chapter: 1\
    on_violation: FAIL
\f0 \
\
---\
\
## 2.2 Governor B: Demo Saturation (Anti "Too Many Examples")\
\
### Purpose\
Prevents bloated example lists that exhaust the listener before the point lands.\
\
### Rule\

\f11 Per insight, per chapter:\
  DEMONSTRATE beats allowed: 3\
  Violation: WARN (default) or FAIL (strict mode)
\f0 \
\
### What It Fixes\
| Chapter | Problem | Current Count | After Cap |\
|---------|---------|---------------|-----------|\
| 1 | Core sentence vignettes | 5 | 3 |\
| 3 | Domain demonstrations | 7 | 3 |\
| 11 | "I am..." statements | 5 | 3 |\
| 11 | "You can..." statements | 6 | 3 |\
\
### Config\

\f11 yaml\
governors:\
  demo_saturation:\
    enabled: true\
    max_per_insight_per_chapter: 3\
    on_violation: WARN  # or FAIL in strict mode\
    strict_mode: false
\f0 \
