# 6. FAILURE MODES\
\
| Failure Mode | Detection | Resolution |\
|--------------|-----------|------------|\
| EXPLAIN cap exceeded | Governor A flags beat_id | Delete beat from template |\
| Demo saturation | Governor B flags beat_id | Delete beat from template or reduce demos |\
| Duplicate block | Governor C flags beat_id + duplicate_of | Delete one of the duplicate beats |\
| Truncation | Governor D flags beat_id | Fix generation bug, regenerate |\
| Unknown insight_id | Validator warns | Add to insight_inventory.yaml |\
| Missing insight_role | Validator warns | Annotate beat in template CSV |\
